response:
I 記得你要求我幫助你架設一個 Captive Portal，讓我給你一些建議：

### 步驟 1：選擇伺服器和程式

*   使用一個伺服器來跑你的 Captive Portal，例如 Apache、Nginx 或是 IIS。
*   選擇 PHP 或 Python 作為後端程式。

### 步驟 2：設定 Captive Portal HTML 模板

#### HTML 模板：

```html
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Captive Portal</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            width: 80%;
            margin: 40px auto;
            text-align: center;
        }

        #login-form {
            width: 50%;
            margin: 20px auto;
            padding: 20px;
            border: 1px solid #ccc;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        #login-form input[type="text"], #login-form input[type="password"] {
            width: 100%;
            height: 40px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            padding: 10px;
            border: 1px solid #ccc;
        }

        #login-form button[type="submit"] {
            width: 100%;
            height: 40px;
            background-color: #4CAF50;
            color: #fff;
            padding: 10px;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            cursor: pointer;
        }

        #login-form button[type="submit"]:hover {
            background-color: #3e8e41;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <h1>Captive Portal</h1>
    <p>Please enter your credentials to access the network.</p>
    <form id="login-form">
        <label for="username">Username:</label>
        <input type="text" id="username" name="username"><br><br>
        <label for="password">Password:</label>
        <input type="password" id="password" name="password"><br><br>
        <button type="submit">Login</button>
    </form>

    <script>
        document.getElementById('login-form').addEventListener('submit', function(event) {
            event.preventDefault();
            var username = document.getElementById('username').value;
            var password = document.getElementById('password').value;

            // send request to backend server
            fetch('/login', {
                method: 'POST',
                headers: {
                    'Content-Type': 'application/json'
                },
                body: JSON.stringify({
                    username: username,
                    password: password
                })
            })
            .then(response => response.json())
            .then(data => {
                if (data.success) {
                    // redirect to destination URL
                    window.location.href = '/destination-url';
                } else {
                    alert('Invalid credentials');
                }
            })
            .catch(error => console.error(error));
        });
    </script>
</body>
</html>
```

### 步驟 3：設定後端程式

#### PHP 程式：

```php
<?php
// configuration
$db_host = 'localhost';
$db_username = 'your_username';
$db_password = 'your_password';
$db_name = 'your_database';

// connect to database
$conn = new mysqli($db_host, $db_username, $db_password, $db_name);

// check connection
if ($conn->connect_error) {
    die("Connection failed: " . $conn->connect_error);
}

// get request data from POST
$username = $_POST['username'];
$password = $_POST['password'];

// hash password before storing in database
$password_hash = password_hash($password, PASSWORD_DEFAULT);

// query to check credentials
$query = "SELECT * FROM users WHERE username = '$username' AND password = '$password_hash'";
$result = $conn->query($query);

// check if credentials are valid
if ($result->num_rows > 0) {
    // redirect to destination URL
    header('Location: /destination-url');
    exit;
} else {
    // return false
    echo json_encode(array('success' => false));
}
$conn->close();
?>
```

#### Python程式：

```python
import sqlite3
from flask import Flask, request, jsonify

app = Flask(__name__)

# configuration
db_host = 'localhost'
db_username = 'your_username'
db_password = 'your_password'
db_name = 'your_database'

# connect to database
conn = sqlite3.connect(db_host)
cursor = conn.cursor()

# create table if not exists
cursor.execute('''
    CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS users (
        id INTEGER PRIMARY KEY,
        username TEXT NOT NULL,
        password TEXT NOT NULL
    )
''')

# get request data from POST
username = request.form['username']
password = request.form['password']

# hash password before storing in database
import hashlib
password_hash = hashlib.sha256(password.encode('utf-8')).hexdigest()

# query to check credentials
cursor.execute("SELECT * FROM users WHERE username = ? AND password = ?", (username, password_hash))

# check if credentials are valid
if cursor.fetchone():
    # redirect to destination URL
    return jsonify({'success': True})
else:
    # return false
    return jsonify({'success': False})

conn.close()
```

### 步驟 4：部署 Captive Portal

1.  将 HTML 模板和後端程式儲存在伺服器上。
2.  啟動 Captive Portal 伺服器，將其設定為 listened 這個端口。

### 步驟 5：測試 Captive Portal

1.  使用一個公司內部 WiFi 熱點的SSID和密碼連入 Captive Portal。
2.  ตรวจสอบ是否能夠登入 Captive Portal成功，得到正確的驗證。

